      • ProtoCodec

        public ProtoCodec(@NotNull
                  @NotNull ProtoCodec.ByteArrayParser<T> byteArrayParser,
                  @NotNull
                  @NotNull ProtoCodec.InputStreamParser<T> inputStreamParser)
        Instantiates a ProtoCodec instance that deserializes messages with the given ProtoCodec.ByteArrayParser.

        The specific parser that is provided defines which protobuf message class this codec is for. For example, new ProtoCodec<>(Protos.Event::parseFrom) instantiates a codec for Event messages.

        Parameters:
        byteArrayParser - The function to use to parse byte[]
        inputStreamParser - The function to use to parse InputStream

        Returns the IANA media type of the serialized message format handled by this object.

        The value returned by this method will be used in the Content-Type and Accept headers for messages sent to and received from Mesos, respectively.
